name: Spaceport Docking Bay (V)
LocationDStext: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force. Your starfighters deploy -1 (or -2 if freighter) here. Immune to [Reflections 3] Ounee Ta.
LocationLStext: May not deploy to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4. Your docking bay transit from here requires 3 Force.
